# Page Template: Dashboard

Reference structure for overview / dashboard pages in **{{ display_name }}**.

Design style: **{{ design_style }}**

---

## Purpose

A dashboard page gives the user a high-level snapshot of the system. It answers "what is happening right now?" It should be scannable in under 10 seconds.

---

