## Empty and Error States

| Scenario | Treatment |
|----------|-----------|
| No data for date range | Illustration + "No data for this period" + link to adjust range |
| API error loading KPIs | Inline error card with "Retry" button |
| API error loading chart | Chart container with error message, rest of page unaffected |
| New account (no events) | Onboarding callout: "Start by creating your first X" |

---

## Responsiveness

| Viewport | Layout |
|----------|--------|
| < 640 px | 1-column stack: KPIs scroll horizontally, charts full-width |
| 640 - 1023 px | 2-column KPI grid, charts full-width |
| >= 1024 px | Full layout as described above |

---

## Performance Notes

- KPI numbers should be visible within 1 s (LCP target)
- Lazy-load charts with `next/dynamic` and `ssr: false` if the chart library is large
- Do not block page render on the activity feed - load it after the above-the-fold content
